# Pre-push hook multi-mirror dedup cache (advisory; recreated on demand).
# Forensic anchor: SP-3a Step 6+7 used --no-verify on 3-of-4 mirror
# pushes because re-running scripts/ci.sh --changed-only against an
# identical SHA was redundant. The hook now caches verified SHAs in
# this file and skips Layer 2 on cache hit. Local-only by design.
.lava-ci-evidence/.pre-push-verified-shas

# Timestamped scripts/ci.sh run-output dirs are local session telemetry,
# not committed evidence. The committed evidence files live at the
# top level of .lava-ci-evidence/ and in named subdirs (sp3a-*/, sp2-*/,
# bluff-hunt/, sixth-law-incidents/, Lava-Android-*/).
.lava-ci-evidence/2026-*/

# Build outputs at any depth (already covered for /build but nested
# modules generate their own build/ dirs)
**/build/
